LogFile.FinalText: It is incredible how much they look like each other. That's the way many think about the two princesses in Denmark. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie, but just as many - if not more - differences. They are both from abroad, are of 'plain decent' and have found each their prince of Denmark - Mary is married to crown prince Frederik and Marie with prince Joachim. Even their names and their looks are incredibly similar. Both are beautiful on a model scale with long, dark hair and large brown eyes. But in spite of the many similarities Mary and Marie are also two independent individuals who have lived and live in each their own way and which has influenced their values and character.
